{"word":"καρπός","slug":"καρπός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰαρπός, ου, ὁ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Skt.\">Skt.</a> assoc; most <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to agricultural produce]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘the product of a living entity’, <b>fruit<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of plants <b><a href='B:470 3:10'>Mt 3:10</a>; <a href='B:470 7:17-19'>7:17-19</a>; <a href='B:470 13:8'>13:8</a>, <a href='B:470 13:26'>26</a>; <a href='B:470 21:19'>21:19</a>, <a href='B:470 21:34'>34</a>, <a href='B:470 21:41'>41</a>; <a href='B:480 4:7'>Mk 4:7</a>; <a href='B:490 6:44'>Lk 6:44</a>; <a href='B:500 12:24'>J 12:24</a>; <a href='B:620 2:6'>2 Ti 2:6</a>; <a href='B:660 5:7'>Js 5:7</a>, <a href='B:660 5:18'>18</a>; <a href='B:730 22:2'>Rv 22:2</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of humans <b><a href='B:490 1:42'>Lk 1:42</a>; <a href='B:510 2:30'>Ac 2:30</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> in imagery of moral-spiritual productivity: by <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ext.\">ext.</a> of 1<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> fruit, produce <a href='B:470 3:8'>Mt 3:8</a>; <a href='B:470 7:20'>7:20</a>; <a href='B:500 4:36'>J 4:36</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in J; <b><a href='B:520 6:21'>Ro 6:21f</a>; <a href='B:650 12:11'>Hb 12:11</a>;</b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> letters. <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on <b>yield/gain <a href='B:500 4:36'>J 4:36</a>; <a href='B:520 1:13'>Ro 1:13</a>; <a href='B:570 1:22'>Phil 1:22</a>; <a href='B:570 4:17'>4:17</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Κάρπος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:καρποφορέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}